1ataniq qaumanirivara, piulijautjutigillugulu;
2piungittulijut ᕾliqpata uvannik akiraqturumalutik uviniga nirijumalugu,
3unataqtukᓮt avatinni ungalusigaluaqpata,
4atausiq qinuarivara atanirngmit, qiniqlugulu nanijumallugu;
5ullumik isuangittuqaliqpat, iglumini saputisimaniaqpaanga;
6maannalu niaqura aaqlurngniaqpara, akiraqtuqtima ilumajima qulaattigut;
7ataniiq nipiga tusaruk nillialiᕅguma: nikagilunga kiulaunnga.
8uqaravit, “kiinara qiniruk,”
9kiiᓁt alaumatinniarngnagu uvannit!
10ataatama anaanamalu qimakkaluaqpanga,
11ataniiq, aqqutingnik ilinniaqtilaunnga;
12akiraqtuqtima pijumajanginnut tuniniarngnanga;
13sapilirajalaurama ukpilaungikkuma ataniup
14ataniq utaqqiguk; kuksasungillutit,
